\/11\/hijab-not-stare-at-women\/","url_meta":{"origin":32609,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Hijab: Men must respect women, not stare at them","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 11, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Al-Fadl was riding with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and a woman from Khash\u2019am came. Al-Fadl began to stare at her and she stared at him. The Prophet made Al-Fadl turn his face in the other direction. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1442, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33732,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/17\/prohibition-describing-sex\/","url_meta":{"origin":32609,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Modesty: Prohibition of verbally describing sexual features","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 17, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA woman should not touch another woman and then describe her figure to her husband as if he were gazing at her.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5240 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":29302,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/13\/weaker-than-man-lower-gaze\/","url_meta":{"origin":32609,"position":2},"title":"Sufyan on Men: Who is weaker than a man unable to lower his gaze?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nu\u2019aym reported: Sufyan al-Thawri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cA woman will pass by a man and he cannot restrain himself from looking at her lustfully although there is no benefit in it. What could be weaker than this?\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304' 7\/68 \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0646\u0639\u064a\u0645 \u0642\u0627\u0644\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34045,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/03\/15\/looking-marriage-candidate\/","url_meta":{"origin":32609,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nikah: Looking at a prospective marriage candidate","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 15, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Mughirah ibn Shu\u2019bah reported: He proposed to a woman in marriage and the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLook at her, for it is the best way to make lasting affection between you.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \u201cSome of the people of knowledge adhered to this tradition. They said:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2862,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/11\/marry-or-fast\/","url_meta":{"origin":32609,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Nikah: Young men who can get married should do so","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 11, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO young men, if you are able to support a wife, get married. Verily, it lowers the gaze and guards chastity. Whoever is not able to do so, he must fast as it will restrain\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40641,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/05\/staring-with-lust\/","url_meta":{"origin":32609,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Zina: Staring with lust is committing adultery","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 5, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Alqamah ibn al-Huwayrith reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe adultery of the two eyes is the lustful gaze.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 18\/8 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064f\u0648\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u0650\u062b\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0632\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2